<section>
  <h2 class="section-title">画面イメージ</h2>
  <div class="screenshot-grid">
    <div class="screenshot-item">
      <div class="screenshot-placeholder has-image">
        <img src="/assets/images/record.png" alt="記録画面">
        <div class="placeholder-content">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
            <circle cx="8.5" cy="8.5" r="1.5"></circle>
            <polyline points="21 15 16 10 5 21"></polyline>
          </svg>
          <span>記録画面</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="screenshot-caption">記録画面</p>
      <p class="screenshot-desc">ワンタップで習慣を記録。<br>シンプルで迷わない操作感。</p>
    </div>
    <div class="screenshot-item">
      <div class="screenshot-placeholder has-image">
        <img src="/assets/images/heatmap.png" alt="ヒートマップ">
        <div class="placeholder-content">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
            <circle cx="8.5" cy="8.5" r="1.5"></circle>
            <polyline points="21 15 16 10 5 21"></polyline>
          </svg>
          <span>ヒートマップ</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="screenshot-caption">ヒートマップ</p>
      <p class="screenshot-desc">継続の軌跡をひと目で確認。<br>色の濃さで達成度がわかる。</p>
    </div>
    <div class="screenshot-item">
      <div class="screenshot-placeholder has-image">
        <img src="/assets/images/review.png" alt="ふりかえり画面">
        <div class="placeholder-content">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
            <circle cx="8.5" cy="8.5" r="1.5"></circle>
            <polyline points="21 15 16 10 5 21"></polyline>
          </svg>
          <span>ふりかえり</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="screenshot-caption">ふりかえり</p>
      <p class="screenshot-desc">実行の積み上げを確認。<br>次につながるヒントを提案。</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  section {
    padding: 48px 0;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 1.375rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-dark);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .screenshot-grid {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 16px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    padding: 0 20px;
  }

  .screenshot-placeholder {
    width: 160px;
    background: var(--bg-white);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
    border: 2px dashed var(--border);
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .screenshot-placeholder img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: none;
  }

  .screenshot-placeholder.has-image {
    border: none;
    height: auto;
  }

  .screenshot-placeholder.has-image img {
    display: block;
  }

  .screenshot-placeholder.has-image .placeholder-content {
    display: none;
  }

  .placeholder-content {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .placeholder-content svg {
    width: 32px;
    height: 32px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    opacity: 0.4;
  }

  .placeholder-content span {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    display: block;
  }

  .screenshot-item {
    text-align: center;
  }

  .screenshot-caption {
    margin-top: 12px;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-dark);
  }

  .screenshot-desc {
    margin-top: 4px;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .screenshot-grid {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 24px;
    }

    .screenshot-item {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 280px;
    }

    .screenshot-placeholder {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: none;
    }
  }
</style>
